reviews.reviewText: I was so excited for this little phone.Realistically , 2.5 inch screen is a disaster.The XS 11 is too slow. I have network cellular but couldnt access lets say tiktok nor Instagram unless on wifi. It hurts to return. Wish it worked better.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Cute but doesn't last
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I loved it it works like a regular sized phone, but it stopped working after a month and I only took it out the box to program and leave until I left the country, it didn't turn on when I tried to use it 😢
